== Tips ==

=== Combat ===

* Exploit elemental weaknesses
* Use correct weapon for enemy
* Check battlefields for grinding

=== Exploration ===

* Use tools on everything
* Bomb suspicious walls
* Claw climb surfaces

=== Companions ===

* They're AI-controlled
* Can't control their actions
* They're temporary (except for final)

